Title: Creamy Sofa for Small Apartments: Ideal for Clothing Stores Homestays and Card Seats
Body (HTML):
Our Products are made to order: 

Products are handcrafted in our factories which means it takes around 10-12 weeks for you to receive your furniture. We do keep our customers informed every step of the way until your furniture reaches your door. 

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

Please ensure you pick the correct variation of the product you want, please read through the description below. If you have any questions, please Email contact@clearance-furniture.com 

Pictures below can be translated using Google Lens on your phone, simply download the app, take the picture that requires translation and press” translate”. 

Please note due to catalogue integration some of the options may come as” free upstairs delivery” ‘’trial’’ ‘’try free for 30 days’’ this will not be the case and product will only be shipped to your door. In addition, each variant is linked with a product picture which generally shows what you will be buying. The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.  

You can view our warranty / returns policy from our menu above.

Body (HTML):
Our Products are made to order: 

Products are handcrafted in our factories which means it takes around 10-12 weeks for you to receive your furniture. We do keep our customers informed every step of the way until your furniture reaches your door. 

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

Please ensure you pick the correct variation of the product you want, please read through the description below. If you have any questions, please Email contact@clearance-furniture.com 

Pictures below can be translated using Google Lens on your phone, simply download the app, take the picture that requires translation and press” translate”. 

Please note due to catalogue integration some of the options may come as” free upstairs delivery” ‘’trial’’ ‘’try free for 30 days’’ this will not be the case and product will only be shipped to your door. In addition, each variant is linked with a product picture which generally shows what you will be buying. The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.  

You can view our warranty / returns policy from our menu above.

Our Products are made to order:

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.

Our Products are made to order: 

Products are handcrafted in our factories which means it takes around 10-12 weeks for you to receive your furniture. We do keep our customers informed every step of the way until your furniture reaches your door. 

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

Please ensure you pick the correct variation of the product you want, please read through the description below. If you have any questions, please Email contact@clearance-furniture.com 

Pictures below can be translated using Google Lens on your phone, simply download the app, take the picture that requires translation and press” translate”. 

Please note due to catalogue integration some of the options may come as” free upstairs delivery” ‘’trial’’ ‘’try free for 30 days’’ this will not be the case and product will only be shipped to your door. In addition, each variant is linked with a product picture which generally shows what you will be buying. The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.  

You can view our warranty / returns policy from our menu above.

The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.

Our Products are made to order: 

Products are handcrafted in our factories which means it takes around 10-12 weeks for you to receive your furniture. We do keep our customers informed every step of the way until your furniture reaches your door. 

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

Please ensure you pick the correct variation of the product you want, please read through the description below. If you have any questions, please Email contact@clearance-furniture.com 

Pictures below can be translated using Google Lens on your phone, simply download the app, take the picture that requires translation and press” translate”. 

Please note due to catalogue integration some of the options may come as” free upstairs delivery” ‘’trial’’ ‘’try free for 30 days’’ this will not be the case and product will only be shipped to your door. In addition, each variant is linked with a product picture which generally shows what you will be buying. The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.

Title: Multi-functional Foldable Sofa Bed: Perfect for Small Apartments and Living Rooms
Body (HTML):
Our Products are made to order:

Products are handcrafted in our factories which means it takes around 10-12 weeks for you to receive your furniture. We do keep our customers informed every step of the way until your furniture reaches your door.

Please read before placing an order:

Unfortunately we are unable to ship to remote islands (e.g., Hawaii or Alaska) we can only ship US Mainland. Please do NOT place an order if you are from a remote region or a segregated island. If you’re from another country, live on the mainland and interested in our products, please send us an email as we will most likely be able to ship to you. Delivery to the USA is $99 per piece and this includes customs charges / taxes/ door to door delivery.

For products such as a 3 seater + 2 seater, these will be treated as 2 pieces. Therefore, the delivery charge will be charged twice.

Please ensure you pick the correct variation of the product you want, please read through the description below. If you have any questions, please Email contact@clearance-furniture.com

Pictures below can be translated using Google Lens on your phone, simply download the app, take the picture that requires translation and press” translate”.

Please note due to catalogue integration some of the options may come as” free upstairs delivery” ‘’trial’’ ‘’try free for 30 days’’ this will not be the case and product will only be shipped to your door. In addition, each variant is linked with a product picture which generally shows what you will be buying. The product price should differ depending on what variant you have chosen, if this doesn't happen please email contact@clearance-furniture.com.

You can view our warranty / returns policy from our menu above.
